Package net.sf.jclec.exprtree.mut

Expression tree encoding mutation operators.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllNodesMutator
    Took each and every node in the computer program and replaced it with another randomly chosen block of the same return type and arity.
    AllNodesMutatorTest
    Unit tests for AllNodesMutatorTest.
    DemoteMutator
    Randomly selected a function node, replacing it with its larger son.
    DemoteMutatorTest
    Unit tests for DemoteMutatorTest.
    GrowMutator
    Randomly select a terminal node in the expression and replace it with a newly generated subtree (of the same return type).
    GrowMutatorTest
    Unit tests for GrowMutatorTest.
    OneNodeMutator
    Randomly select a node in the expression and replace it with another randomly chosen block of the same return type and arity.
    OneNodeMutatorTest
    Unit tests for OneNodeMutatorTest.
    PromoteMutator
    A random subtree, T', is selected and replaced by a random function node.
    PromoteMutatorTest
    Unit tests for PromoteMutatorTest.
    SubtreeMutator
    Subtree mutator.
    SubTreeMutatorTest
    Unit tests for SubTreeMutatorTest.
    TruncMutator
    Randomly select a function node in the expression and replace it with a terminal (of the same return type), thus effectively clipping the tree at that node.
    TruncMutatorTest
    Unit tests for TrucMutatorTest.
